{"type":"message","id":"7537f8ea","parentId":"b237e4f4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:59:29.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从日志可以看出几个问题：\n1. API 密钥错误（403 invalid api-key）\n2. OpenRouter 余额不足\n3. API 限流（429）\n\n这些都是模型调用的问题，不是飞书连接本身的问题。让我检查飞书 OAuth 授权状态和 WebSocket 连接状态。让我尝试调用 feishu_oauth 工具来检查授权状态。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！日志显示有多个 API 错误：\n- **403 invalid api-key** - API 密钥无效\n- **OpenRouter 余额不足** \n- **429 API 限流**\n\n这些都是模型调用失败，不是飞书连接问题。让我检查飞书 OAuth 授权状态，这通常是\"没反应\"的根本原因：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_20771be1205c4018b648a32f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/sessions/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":208,"cacheRead":27798,"cacheWrite":711,"totalTokens":28723,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000058240000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000589}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774583965527,"responseId":"msg_851ce6f5-f282-4ec4-9bda-43351671e995"}}
